ci%2C%20che%20spesso%20gli%20suggerivano%20la%20prossima%20mossa%20o%20lo%20avvertivano%20di%20un%20pericolo%20imminente.%20Per%20tutti%20era%20solo%20pazzo%20ma%20lui%2C%20confidando%20in%20quelle%20voci%2C%20era%20sopravvissuto%20pi%C3%B9%20volte%20a%20situazioni%20apparentemente%20senza%20uscita.%20Col%20tempo%20ci%20fu%20anche%20chi%20inizi%C3%B2%20a%20pensare%20che%20avesse%20subito%20una%20mutazione%2C%20e%20che%20Skull%20fosse%20in%20grado%20di%20vedere%20il%20futuro.%20Forse%20le%20voci%20non%20lo%20avvertirono%20dell%E2%80%99incendio%20che%20uccise%20i%20suoi%20genitori%2C%20o%20forse%20lo%20fecero%20e%20lui%20scelse%20di%20ignorarle.%20Rimasto%20solo%2C%20ma%20finalmente%20libero%2C%20si%20dedic%C3%B2%20a%20ci%C3%B2%20che%20pi%C3%B9%20lo%20aveva%20affascinato%20nella%20sua%20giovane%20vita.%20Inizio%20una%20lotta%20perch%C3%A9%20tutti%20sapessero%20le%20vere%20condizioni%20in%20cui%20vivevano%20i%20cittadini%20pi%C3%B9%20poveri%20di%20strutture%2C%20pubblic%C3%B2%20articoli%20sul%20degrado%2C%20sulle%20gang%20e%20sulla%20corruzione%20ai%20livelli%20pi%C3%B9%20bassi%2C%20quasi%20sempre%20incappando%20in%20scontri%20armati%20per%20riuscirci.%20Per%20continuare%20questa%20sua%20crociata%2C%20per%C3%B2%2C%20aveva%20bisogno%20di%20fama%20e%20di%20attenzione%2C%20di%20qualcosa%20che%20lo%20rendesse%20unico.%20Si%20tatu%C3%B2%20quindi%20un%20teschio%20sul%20volto%2C%20ad%20emulare%20il%20proprio%20nome.%20Questo%20gli%20avrebbe%20reso%20l%E2%80%99intrufolarsi%20molto%20pi%C3%B9%20difficile%2C%20ma%20non%20serve%20mentire%20o%20fingersi%20qualcun%20altro%20quando%20nessuno%20sa%20che%20lo%20stai%20spiando.%20Consigliato%20dalle%20voci%2C%20armato%20delle%20sue%20lame%20e%20della%20sua%20macchina%20fotografica%2C%20adesso%20Skull%20si%20%C3%A8%20unito%20all%E2%80%99SGC%2C%20convinto%20che%20questo%20lo%20porter%C3%A0%20ad%20una%20verit%C3%A0%20ancora%20pi%C3%B9%20sconvolgente.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(Le%20voci%20non%20sono%20state%20introdotte%20nel%20Background%20per%20ri